fields.name: Foie Gras Brioche
fields.description: Buttery Brioche Topped With Rich Foie Gras And Fig Jam
fields.recipe: Brioche slices toasted. Foie gras sliced and lightly seared. Brioche spread with fig jam or chutney. Foie gras placed on top. Garnished with microgreens. Served immediately.

fields.name: Truffle Mushroom Toast
fields.description: Sourdough Toast With SautΘed Wild Mushrooms And Black Truffle Oil
fields.recipe: Mushrooms sliced and sautΘed in butter. Truffle oil added. Bread slices toasted. Mushrooms piled on toast. Garnished with fresh herbs. Served warm.

fields.name: Lobster Roll On Buttered Brioche
fields.description: Fresh Lobster Salad In A Toasted Brioche Bun With Lemon Aioli
fields.recipe: Lobster meat chopped and tossed with mayo, lemon juice, and seasoning. Brioche buns buttered and toasted. Lobster mixture piled into buns. Served immediately.

fields.name: Duck Confit Rustic Sandwich
fields.description: Slow-Cooked Duck Leg With Caramelized Onions And Arugula
fields.recipe:
Duck legs cooked slowly in fat until tender. Meat shredded. Rustic bread sliced and toasted. Dijon mustard spread on bread.

Shredded duck piled on bread. Topped with arugula and caramelized onions. Sandwich assembled and served immediately.

fields.name: Burrata & Tomato Crostini
fields.description: Creamy Burrata Cheese With Heirloom Tomatoes And Basil Oil
fields.recipe:
Baguette: sliced, brushed with olive oil, toasted. Tomatoes: chopped, seasoned with salt, pepper, olive oil, basil. Burrata: torn gently.

Toasted bread topped with tomatoes. Burrata placed on top. Drizzled with olive oil. Served immediately.

fields.name: Oysters Rockefeller
fields.description: Fresh Oysters Baked With Spinach, Butter, And Parmesan
fields.recipe: Oysters shucked, shells reserved. Spinach, parsley, and green herbs chopped and sautΘed with garlic and butter. Breadcrumbs and Parmesan mixed in. Oyster shells filled with oyster and herb mixture. Topped with breadcrumb mix. Broiled until golden and bubbly. Served hot.

fields.name: Tuna Tartare With Avocado And Citrus
fields.description: Finely Diced Tuna, Creamy Avocado, And A Zesty Citrus Dressing
fields.recipe: Fresh tuna diced finely. Avocado diced. Citrus segments prepared. Tuna mixed with lemon juice, olive oil, salt, and pepper. Layered or combined with avocado and citrus. Served chilled, garnished with herbs.

fields.name: Carpaccio Di Manzo
fields.description: Thinly Sliced Raw Beef, Peppery Arugula, And Shaved Parmesan
fields.recipe:
Beef tenderloin: chilled, sliced paper-thin. Arugula: washed, dried. Parmesan: shaved. Lemon juice and olive oil: whisked into dressing.

Beef arranged on plate. Arugula placed on top. Dressed lightly. Topped with Parmesan. Seasoned with salt and pepper. Served cold.

fields.name: Caviar & Blinis
fields.description: Premium Caviar Served With Delicate Blinis And Sour Cream
fields.recipe:
Flour, eggs, milk, and yeast mixed into batter. Rested until bubbly. Spoonfuls cooked on hot griddle until golden. Blinis cooled.

Sour cream dolloped on blinis. Caviar placed on top. Garnished with chopped chives. Served immediately.

fields.name: Smoked Salmon & Dill Cream
fields.description: Smoked Salmon On Rye Crackers With Dill-Infused Cream Cheese
fields.recipe: Smoked salmon sliced thin. Cream cheese softened. Fresh dill chopped finely. Cream cheese mixed with dill and lemon juice. Spread on toast or crackers. Topped with smoked salmon slices. Garnished with dill sprigs. Served chilled.

fields.name: Lobster Bisque With Cognac
fields.description: Smooth Lobster Soup Finished With A Splash Of Cognac
fields.recipe:
Lobster shells roasted. Onion, carrot, and celery sautΘed. Tomato paste added and cooked briefly. Cognac flamed in pan. Lobster shells and vegetables simmered with water to make stock. Strained broth reduced.

Lobster meat chopped. Cream and butter added to broth. Bisque simmered gently. Seasoned with salt and pepper. Served hot.

fields.name: Wild Mushroom & Truffle Oil
fields.description: Silky Mushroom Soup Enhanced By Aromatic Truffle Oil
fields.recipe: Wild mushrooms cleaned and sliced. SautΘed in butter until tender. Seasoned with salt and pepper. Finished with a drizzle of truffle oil. Served warm.

fields.name: Asparagus Soup With Cream
fields.description: Fresh Asparagus Puree Topped With Tangy Chive Cream
fields.recipe: Trim the tough ends of the asparagus; cut the stalks into pieces. Chop the onion; sautΘ in butter until soft. Add the asparagus; cook for a few minutes. Pour in vegetable broth. Bring to a boil; simmer until asparagus is tender. Blend until smooth. Add cream; stir well. Season with salt and pepper. Heat gently; do not boil. Serve warm; garnish with herbs if desired.

fields.name: Pumpkin VeloutΘ With Toasted Pepitas
fields.description: Velvety Pumpkin Soup Garnished With Crunchy Toasted Seeds
fields.recipe:
Pumpkin peeled, diced, and cooked in broth until soft. Pureed until smooth. Cream added and heated gently. Seasoned with salt, pepper, and nutmeg.

Pepitas toasted in dry pan until crisp. Soup ladled into bowls. Topped with toasted pepitas. Served warm.

fields.name: Cauliflower Soup & Crisp
fields.description: Rich Cauliflower Soup Served With A Crispy Parmesan Chip
fields.recipe:
Cauliflower: chopped. Onion and garlic: sautΘed in butter. Cauliflower added, cooked briefly. Vegetable broth poured in. Simmered until soft. Blended until smooth. Cream stirred in. Seasoned with salt and pepper.

Thin cauliflower slices: brushed with oil, roasted until crisp.

Soup ladled into bowls. Crisps placed on top. Served hot.

fields.name: Choc Fondant With Raspberry
fields.description: Warm Molten Chocolate Cake With Fresh Raspberry Sauce
fields.recipe:
Chocolate and butter melted together. Eggs and sugar whisked until pale. Flour added, folded in gently. Batter poured into molds. Baked at high temperature for 10û12 minutes. Center should remain molten.

Raspberries rinsed. Served with fondant.

fields.name: CrΦme Br√lΘe With Vanilla
fields.description: Classic Custard Dessert With A Caramelized Madagascar Vanilla Sugar Crust
fields.recipe:
Heavy cream and vanilla bean heated until simmering. Egg yolks and sugar whisked until pale. Hot cream slowly added to yolks, whisking constantly. Mixture strained and poured into ramekins. Baked in water bath until set.

Chilled. Sugar sprinkled on top. Caramelized with torch until golden and crisp. Served cold.

fields.name: Tarte Tatin With Calvados Caramel
fields.description: Upside-Down Caramelized Apple Tart With Calvados Brandy
fields.recipe: Apples peeled, cored, and halved. Sugar and butter melted in pan to form caramel. Calvados added to caramel. Apples arranged in caramel. Puff pastry placed over apples. Baked until pastry is golden. Warmed briefly, inverted onto plate. Served immediately.

fields.name: Pistachio Opera Cake
fields.description: Layered Almond Sponge With Pistachio Cream And Dark Chocolate
fields.recipe: Almond sponge cake baked in thin layers. Pistachio buttercream prepared. Coffee syrup brushed on cake layers. Layers alternated with pistachio buttercream and ganache. Cake chilled to set. Finished with glossy chocolate glaze. Served sliced.

fields.name: Lemon SoufflΘ With Blueberry
fields.description: Light And Airy Lemon SoufflΘ Served With Sweet Blueberry Sauce
fields.recipe:
Lemon zest and juice combined. Egg yolks and sugar whisked until pale. Egg whites whipped to stiff peaks. Yolks folded into whites gently. Mixture poured into buttered ramekins. Baked until puffed and golden.

Blueberries rinsed. SoufflΘs served immediately with blueberries.

fields.name: Classic French 75
fields.description: Elegant Cocktail Of Gin, Champagne, Lemon Juice, And Sugar, Shaken And Served Chilled In A Flute
fields.recipe: Gin, lemon juice, and simple syrup shaken with ice. Strained into a flute glass. Topped with chilled Champagne. Garnished with a lemon twist. Served immediately.

fields.name: Barrel-Aged Negroni
fields.description: Aged Blend Of Gin, Campari, And Sweet Vermouth With A Smooth Oak Finish
fields.recipe: Combine equal parts gin, Campari, and sweet vermouth. Pour into an oak barrel and seal tightly. Store in a cool, dark place and age for 4û6 weeks, rotating occasionally. Strain, transfer to a bottle, and chill. Pour over ice, garnish with orange peel, and serve.

fields.name: Passion Fruit & Basil Martini
fields.description: Vodka-Based Martini With Passion Fruit PurΘe, Basil Syrup, And Lime Juice ù Tropical And Aromatic
fields.recipe: Vodka, passion fruit juice, and simple syrup shaken with ice. Fresh basil leaves muddled gently. Mixture strained into chilled martini glass. Garnished with basil leaf. Served immediately.

fields.name: Smoked Old Fashioned
fields.description: Bourbon Stirred With Demerara Syrup And Bitters, Served Under A Dome Of Hickory Smoke
fields.recipe: Sugar cube soaked with bitters. Muddled gently. Bourbon added with ice. Stirred until chilled. Glass smoked using wood chips or smoke gun. Cocktail poured into smoked glass. Garnished with orange peel. Served immediately.

fields.name: Spiced Mango Ginger Fizz
fields.description: Fresh Mango PurΘe, Ginger Syrup, Lemon Juice, And Soda ù Shaken Into A Refreshing And Tangy Mocktail
fields.recipe: Mango puree combined with ginger syrup and lime juice. Shaken with ice. Strained into glass. Topped with sparkling water. Garnished with lime wedge and mint. Served immediately.

fields.name: Chilean Sea Bass With Saffron
fields.description: Delicate Sea Bass Served With Creamy Saffron Reduction
fields.recipe: Soak saffron in warm broth. Season Chilean sea bass with salt and pepper. Heat oil, sear fish until golden crust forms. Pour in saffron broth, simmer gently until cooked through. Serve with sauce.

fields.name: Grilled Branzino & Herb Butter
fields.description: Whole Mediterranean Sea Bass Grilled And Basted With Herbs
fields.recipe: Branzino cleaned and scored. Seasoned with salt and pepper. Grilled until skin is crisp and flesh opaque. Herb butter ù softened butter mixed with chopped parsley, garlic, lemon zest. Fish brushed with herb butter. Served immediately.

fields.name: Black Cod With Miso Glaze
fields.description: Rich Black Cod Marinated In Sweet Miso And Broiled
fields.recipe:
White miso, mirin, sake, sugar: mixed until smooth. Glaze: simmered, cooled. Black cod: marinated in glaze for 24 to 48 hours.

Oven preheated. Excess marinade wiped off. Fish broiled until caramelized and flaky.

Served hot, optionally with rice or pickled vegetables.

fields.name: Halibut With Fennel & Citrus
fields.description: Tender Halibut With Aromatic Fennel And Bright Citrus Notes
fields.recipe: Halibut fillets seasoned with salt and pepper. Fennel thinly sliced. Citrus segments prepared. Olive oil heated in pan. Halibut seared until golden and cooked through. Fennel sautΘed until tender. Plate fish, top with fennel and citrus. Drizzle with olive oil. Serve warm.

fields.name: Tuna Steak & Wasabi Mash
fields.description: Seared Tuna Served Atop Creamy Mashed Potatoes With Wasabi Kick
fields.recipe: Tuna steak seasoned with salt and pepper. Seared quickly on high heat until rare inside. Potatoes boiled and mashed. Wasabi paste mixed into mash. Tuna plated alongside wasabi mash. Served immediately.

fields.name: Wagyu Beef Burger With Foie Gras
fields.description: Juicy Wagyu Patty Topped With Seared Foie Gras And Truffle Aioli
fields.recipe:
Wagyu beef formed into patties, seasoned. Patties seared to desired doneness. Foie gras sliced and quickly seared. Burger buns toasted.

Buns spread with mustard or aioli. Patties placed on buns. Topped with foie gras. Served immediately.

fields.name: Black Truffle Cheeseburger
fields.description: Angus Beef With Melted Cheese And Shaved Black Truffles
fields.recipe:
Ground beef: formed into patties, seasoned. Patties seared until a crust forms, cooked to desired doneness. Brioche buns: toasted.

Black truffle aioli spread on buns. Patties topped with melted cheese, placed on buns. Caramelized onions added. Optional arugula or lettuce layered.

Top bun placed. Served immediately.

fields.name: Lamb Burger With Mint Yogurt Sauce
fields.description: Spiced Lamb Patty Served With Fresh Mint Yogurt Dressing
fields.recipe: Ground lamb seasoned, formed into patties. Patties grilled or pan-seared until cooked through. Yogurt, chopped mint, and lemon juice mixed to make sauce. Burger buns toasted. Patties placed on buns. Topped with mint yogurt sauce. Served immediately.

fields.name: Duck Burger With Caramelized Onions
fields.description: Rich Duck Meat Topped With Sweet Onions And Creamy Sauce
fields.recipe:
Ground duck seasoned, formed into patties. Patties seared until cooked through. Onions sliced thin, caramelized slowly in butter. Burger buns toasted.

Buns spread with mustard or mayo. Patties placed on buns. Topped with caramelized onions. Served immediately.

fields.name: Lobster Burger With Garlic Aioli
fields.description: Fresh Lobster Patty Dressed With Garlic Aioli And Greens
fields.recipe:
Cooked lobster meat chopped. Mixed with mayonnaise, lemon juice, and seasonings. Formed into patties. Patties seared until golden and heated through. Burger buns toasted.

Garlic aioli ù mayonnaise, garlic, lemon juice ù whisked until smooth. Buns spread with aioli. Patties placed on buns. Topped with lettuce or greens. Served immediately.

fields.name: Escargots └ La Bourguignonne
fields.description: Snails Baked In Garlic Herb Butter And Parsley
fields.recipe: Snails cleaned and removed from shells. Garlic, parsley, and butter finely chopped and mixed. Snail shells filled with snails and herb butter. Baked until butter is bubbly and golden. Served hot with crusty bread.

fields.name: Crispy Calamari With Lemon Aioli
fields.description: Lightly Fried Squid Rings With Tangy Lemon Mayo
fields.recipe:
Calamari rings tossed in flour and seasoning. Deep-fried until golden and crisp. Drained on paper towel.

Aioli ù mayonnaise, garlic, lemon juice ù whisked until smooth. Served alongside calamari. Garnished with lemon wedges.

fields.name: Duck Spring Rolls With Plum Sauce
fields.description: Crispy Rolls Filled With Tender Duck And Served With Sweet Sauce
fields.recipe:
Cooked duck meat shredded. Rice paper wrappers softened in warm water. Fillers ù shredded duck, julienned vegetables, herbs ù placed on wrapper. Rolled tightly.

Plum sauce prepared separately or store-bought. Spring rolls served with plum sauce for dipping.

fields.name: Mini Beef Wellington Bites
fields.description: Bite-Sized Puff Pastries With Tender Beef And Mushroom Duxelles
fields.recipe: Beef tenderloin cut into small cubes. Mushrooms and shallots finely chopped and sautΘed. Puff pastry rolled and cut into small squares. Beef cubes seared briefly. Mushroom mixture spread on pastry squares. Beef placed on top, wrapped and sealed. Baked until golden and beef cooked to desired doneness. Served warm.

fields.name: Seared Scallops With Pea PurΘe
fields.description: Perfectly Seared Scallops Served On Vibrant Pea PurΘe
fields.recipe: Scallops patted dry and seasoned. Oil heated in pan. Scallops seared until golden and opaque. Peas cooked until tender. Peas blended with cream and butter until smooth. PurΘe seasoned with salt and pepper. Scallops plated over pea purΘe. Served immediately.

fields.name: Wagyu Ribeye With Red Wine Sauce
fields.description: Marbled Ribeye Steak Drizzled With Rich Red Wine Sauce
fields.recipe:
Wagyu ribeye seasoned with salt and pepper. Seared in hot pan to desired doneness. Rested before serving.

Red wine, shallots, and beef stock reduced to sauce. Butter whisked in for gloss. Sauce poured over steak. Served immediately.

fields.name: Roasted Rack Of Lamb With Herb Crust
fields.description: Tender Lamb Rack Roasted With Rosemary And Garlic Crust
fields.recipe: Rack of lamb trimmed and scored. Herb crust made from parsley, rosemary, garlic, breadcrumbs, and olive oil. Lamb seasoned with salt and pepper. Herb crust pressed onto lamb. Roasted until desired doneness. Rested before slicing. Served warm.

fields.name: Beef Tenderloin With BΘarnaise
fields.description: Juicy Tenderloin Paired With Classic BΘarnaise
fields.recipe:
Beef Tenderloin: Trim and tie the beef tenderloin. Season generously with salt and pepper. Sear the tenderloin in a hot pan, browning it on all sides. Transfer it to the oven and roast to your desired doneness. Allow the beef to rest before slicing.

BΘarnaise Sauce: Combine shallots, tarragon, and vinegar in a saucepan and simmer until the mixture is reduced. Strain the reduction, discarding the solids.

In a separate bowl, whisk egg yolks over gentle heat. Slowly add the strained reduction to the egg yolks while continuously whisking. Gradually incorporate melted butter, stirring until the sauce thickens. Finish the sauce with freshly chopped tarragon.
To Serve: Slice the beef tenderloin and top with the BΘarnaise sauce. Serve immediately.

fields.name: Slow-Cooked Porchetta With Fennel
fields.description: Crispy Pork Roast Infused With Fennel And Herbs
fields.recipe: Pork belly scored and seasoned with salt, pepper, fennel seeds, garlic, and herbs. Rolled tightly and tied. Slow-roasted until crispy outside and tender inside. Fennel bulbs roasted or sautΘed as side. Porchetta sliced and served with fennel.

fields.name: Veal Chop & Morel Sauce
fields.description: Succulent Veal Chop Topped With Creamy Morel Sauce
fields.recipe: Veal chop seasoned with salt and pepper. Seared until golden and cooked to desired doneness. Morel mushrooms cleaned and sautΘed in butter. Shallots added and cooked until soft. Cream and stock poured in, reduced to sauce. Sauce poured over veal chop. Served immediately.

fields.name: Lobster Ravioli With Saffron Cream
fields.description: Handmade Ravioli Stuffed With Lobster In Saffron Sauce
fields.recipe:
Ravioli dough rolled thin. Lobster meat chopped and mixed with ricotta and seasonings. Filling placed on dough, sealed into ravioli.

Saffron-infused cream sauce prepared by heating cream with saffron. Ravioli boiled until al dente. Drained and tossed in saffron cream. Served hot.

fields.name: Truffle Tagliatelle With Parmesan
fields.description: Fresh Pasta Tossed With Black Truffle And Parmesan Shavings
fields.recipe: Tagliatelle cooked until al dente. Butter and truffle oil melted together. Pasta tossed in truffle butter. Parmesan cheese grated and mixed in. Seasoned with salt and pepper. Served immediately.

fields.name: Wagyu Bolognese Pappardelle
fields.description: Wide Noodles With Rich Wagyu Meat Sauce
fields.recipe: Wagyu beef minced and browned. Onion, carrot, and celery finely chopped and sautΘed. Tomato paste and crushed tomatoes added. Simmered slowly with herbs and red wine. Pappardelle pasta cooked al dente. Sauce tossed with pasta. Served topped with grated Parmesan.

fields.name: Ink Spaghetti & Sea Urchin
fields.description: Squid Ink Pasta Served With Fresh Sea Urchin And Herbs
fields.recipe: Spaghetti cooked until al dente. Garlic and chili sautΘed in olive oil. Sea urchin roe gently folded into sauce. Cooked pasta tossed with sauce. Seasoned with salt and pepper. Served immediately.

fields.name: Spinach And Ricotta Cannelloni
fields.description: Pasta Tubes Filled With Ricotta And Spinach Baked In BΘchamel
fields.recipe: Spinach cooked and drained. Ricotta cheese mixed with spinach, garlic, and seasoning. Cannelloni tubes filled with mixture. Tomato sauce spread in baking dish. Filled tubes placed on sauce. More sauce and grated cheese added on top. Baked until bubbly and golden. Served hot.

fields.name: Tomato & Burrata Salad With Basil
fields.description: Fresh Tomatoes With Creamy Burrata And Basil Drizzle
fields.recipe: Tomatoes sliced. Burrata torn into pieces. Fresh basil leaves washed and torn. Tomatoes arranged on plate. Burrata placed on top. Basil scattered over. Drizzled with olive oil and balsamic vinegar. Seasoned with salt and pepper. Served fresh.

fields.name: Caesar Salad & Anchovies
fields.description: Classic Caesar With Premium Anchovies And Parmesan Shards
fields.recipe:
Romaine lettuce: washed, dried, torn. Anchovy fillets: minced. Garlic: crushed. Egg yolk, Dijon mustard, lemon juice: whisked. Olive oil added slowly. Parmesan grated into dressing.

Bread: cubed, toasted into croutons. Lettuce tossed with dressing. Anchovies and croutons added. Topped with more Parmesan. Served chilled.

fields.name: Beet & Goat Cheese Salad
fields.description: Roasted Beets Paired With Tangy Goat Cheese And Crunchy Nuts
fields.recipe:
Beets: roasted until tender, peeled, sliced. Arugula: washed, dried. Goat cheese: crumbled. Walnuts: toasted. Dressing: olive oil, balsamic vinegar, mustard, salt, pepper, whisked.

Beets placed on a plate. Arugula added. Topped with goat cheese and walnuts. Drizzled with dressing. Served cold.

fields.name: Kale & Quinoa With Pomegranate
fields.description: Nutritious Kale And Quinoa Tossed With Sweet Pomegranate Seeds
fields.recipe: Quinoa rinsed and cooked until fluffy. Kale chopped and massaged with olive oil and lemon juice. Pomegranate seeds prepared. Quinoa and kale tossed together. Pomegranate seeds sprinkled on top. Seasoned with salt and pepper. Served cold or at room temperature.

fields.name: Lobster Avocado Salad With Citrus
fields.description: Chunks Of Lobster And Creamy Avocado In Zesty Dressing
fields.recipe: Cooked lobster meat chopped. Avocado diced. Citrus segments prepared. Mixed greens washed and dried. Lobster, avocado, citrus, and greens tossed gently. Dressing made from olive oil, lemon juice, salt, and pepper drizzled over salad. Served chilled.

fields.name: Truffle Mashed Potatoes
fields.description: Creamy Mashed Potatoes Infused With Black Truffle Oil
fields.recipe: Potatoes peeled and boiled until tender. Drained and mashed. Butter and cream warmed and mixed in. Truffle oil added to taste. Salt and pepper seasoned. Served hot.

fields.name: Grilled Asparagus With Hollandaise
fields.description: Charred Asparagus Spears Topped With Rich Hollandaise Sauce
fields.recipe: Asparagus trimmed, tossed with olive oil, salt, and pepper. Grilled until tender and slightly charred. Hollandaise sauce made by whisking egg yolks, melted butter, lemon juice, and seasoning over gentle heat until thickened. Asparagus plated and topped with hollandaise. Served warm.

fields.name: Parmesan Risotto
fields.description: Creamy Risotto Cooked With Parmesan Cheese
fields.recipe: Arborio rice toasted in butter and olive oil. Onion finely chopped and sautΘed. Warm broth added gradually, stirred constantly. Cooked until creamy and al dente. Parmesan cheese grated and stirred in. Seasoned with salt and pepper. Served hot.

fields.name: Roasted Brussels Sprouts With Pancetta
fields.description: Crispy Sprouts Roasted With Salty Pancetta Bits
fields.recipe: Brussels sprouts trimmed and halved. Pancetta diced. Olive oil tossed with sprouts and pancetta. Seasoned with salt and pepper. Spread on baking sheet. Roasted until crispy and browned. Served hot.

fields.name: SautΘed Wild Mushrooms With Garlic
fields.description: Mix Of Wild Mushrooms SautΘed In Garlic Butter
fields.recipe: Wild mushrooms cleaned and sliced. Olive oil and butter heated in pan. Garlic minced and added. Mushrooms sautΘed until tender and browned. Seasoned with salt, pepper, and fresh herbs. Served hot.

fields.name: French Onion & GruyΦre Toast
fields.description: Caramelized Onion Broth Topped With Melted GruyΦre And Toast
fields.recipe: Onions thinly sliced, caramelized slowly in butter. Baguette slices toasted. Caramelized onions spread on bread. GruyΦre cheese grated and sprinkled on top. Toasted under broiler until cheese melts and browns. Served hot.

fields.name: Bouillabaisse Fish Soup
fields.description: Rich Seafood Stew With Saffron And Fresh Herbs
fields.recipe:
Onion, leek, fennel, garlic: sliced and sautΘed in olive oil. Tomatoes, orange peel, saffron added. Fish bones and heads placed in pot. Water poured over, brought to a boil. Simmered, impurities skimmed. Bay leaf, thyme, peppercorns added. Cooked for 30 to 40 minutes. Strained, broth reserved.

Firm white fish, mussels, prawns added to hot broth. Simmered until just cooked. Rouille prepared separately.

Soup ladled into bowls. Seafood arranged on top. Served with rouille and toasted bread.

fields.name: Tomato Gazpacho With Basil Oil
fields.description: Chilled Tomato Soup With Aromatic Basil Drizzle
fields.recipe:
Ripe tomatoes, cucumber, bell pepper, garlic, and onion chopped and blended until smooth. Olive oil and vinegar added, then seasoned with salt and pepper. Chilled in the fridge.

For the basil oil, blend basil leaves with olive oil.

Serve the gazpacho cold, drizzled with basil oil.

fields.name: Beef ConsommΘ Dumplings
fields.description: Clear Beef Broth Served With Delicate Herb Dumplings
fields.recipe:
Roast beef bones and meat until browned. Add onion, carrot, celery, bay leaf, and peppercorns. Cover with cold water, bring to a slow simmer. To clarify, add whisked minced beef, mirepoix, and egg whites. Simmer until a "raft" forms. Strain, reserve clear consommΘ.

For dumplings: mix flour, egg, and water into dough. Knead, rest. Roll thin, cut into rounds. Filling: minced beef, onion, garlic, herbs ù season. Place in center, seal tightly. Boil dumplings until tender.

To serve: gently reheat consommΘ, pour into bowls. Add dumplings. Serve hot.

fields.name: Sweet Corn Chowder With Bacon
fields.description: Creamy Corn Soup With Smoky Bacon Bits
fields.recipe: Bacon diced and cooked until crisp. Onion and celery sautΘed in bacon fat. Potatoes and corn kernels added. Chicken broth poured in. Simmered until vegetables are tender. Cream stirred in. Seasoned with salt and pepper. Served hot, topped with crispy bacon.

fields.name: Ratatouille Provencal
fields.description: Traditional Vegetable Stew With Zucchini, Eggplant, And Peppers
fields.recipe: Eggplant, zucchini, bell peppers, tomatoes diced. Onion and garlic sautΘed in olive oil. Vegetables added in layers, cooked slowly. Herbs de Provence, salt, and pepper added. Simmered until tender and flavors melded. Served warm or at room temperature.

fields.name: Grilled Artichokes With Lemon Aioli
fields.description: Tender Artichokes Chargrilled And Served With Tangy Aioli
fields.recipe: Artichokes trimmed, boiled until tender. Halved and brushed with olive oil. Grilled until charred. Aioli ù mayonnaise, garlic, lemon juice ù whisked until smooth. Artichokes served with lemon aioli for dipping

fields.name: Roasted Cauliflower & Romesco
fields.description: Thick Cauliflower Slices Roasted And Topped With Nutty Sauce
fields.recipe:
Cauliflower florets tossed with olive oil, salt, and pepper. Roasted until golden and tender.

Romesco sauce made from roasted red peppers, almonds, garlic, olive oil, and vinegar, blended until smooth.

Cauliflower plated and drizzled with romesco. Served warm.

fields.name: Fennel With Orange & Thyme
fields.description: Soft Fennel Cooked With Citrus And Fragrant Thyme
fields.recipe: Fennel bulbs sliced. Orange zest and juice prepared. Olive oil heated in pan. Fennel sautΘed until tender. Orange juice and thyme added. Cooked until liquid reduces. Seasoned with salt and pepper. Served warm.

fields.name: Honey-Glazed Baby Carrots
fields.description: Sweet Baby Carrots Grilled And Finished With Honey Glaze
fields.recipe: Baby carrots peeled and trimmed. Butter and honey melted together in pan. Carrots added and tossed in glaze. Cooked over medium heat until tender and shiny. Seasoned with salt and pepper. Served warm.

fields.name: Very Thinly Sliced Raw Beef Tenderloin
